  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2835110/extras/f4cb66c0e354673a535e1c8c1abe7c5a.poster.avif?t=1761200550\" width=600 height=120 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2835110/extras/f4cb66c0e354673a535e1c8c1abe7c5a.webm?t=1761200550\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2835110/extras/f4cb66c0e354673a535e1c8c1abe7c5a.mp4?t=1761200550\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Save the world by fishing!  A new pixel open world action RPG! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This is the story of two young men who set out on an adventure to fish for the Sea'Az, the marine creatures of this world. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2835110/extras/d9a465270c6318894a654acec47e9c1c.webp?t=1761200550\" width=600 height=54 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >To catch Sea'Az, perform a successful “Gauge Action”. If you stop the bar at the “Hit Area” or “Critical Area” in the gauge at the right time, you can damage Sea'Az. Successful fishing is achieved by continuing to inflict damage and reducing the HP to 0! Be careful, as there are SeaAZ with more powerful individual “gauge gimmick”.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2835110/extras/9e78d2977609086837522bcedf859946.poster.avif?t=1761200550\" width=600 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2835110/extras/9e78d2977609086837522bcedf859946.webm?t=1761200550\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2835110/extras/9e78d2977609086837522bcedf859946.mp4?t=1761200550\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2835110/extras/e0acde8da57916a16237a8d7b31e727a.webp?t=1761200550\" width=600 height=54 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You can create equipment (fishing rods and hooks) using materials obtained from the Sea'Az you catch. By creating strong equipment, you can take advantage of the fishing action.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2835110/extras/f50704538bd5bd307c2d0bb5426c1e2f.poster.avif?t=1761200550\" width=600 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2835110/extras/f50704538bd5bd307c2d0bb5426c1e2f.webm?t=1761200550\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2835110/extras/f50704538bd5bd307c2d0bb5426c1e2f.mp4?t=1761200550\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2835110/extras/d52f6a37922ee5d1e2d32df01b95db9e.webp?t=1761200550\" width=600 height=54 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Rod and Axel go on an adventurous journey together.<br>Let him do all the fishing for Sea'Az and stripping of materials.<br> Let Axel take care of everything, such as removing obstacles along the way.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2835110/extras/57b4671a7661b73b9c0a9fec5fa1ee47.poster.avif?t=1761200550\" width=600 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2835110/extras/57b4671a7661b73b9c0a9fec5fa1ee47.webm?t=1761200550\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2835110/extras/57b4671a7661b73b9c0a9fec5fa1ee47.mp4?t=1761200550\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2835110/extras/c4e9cccf4f4ee26f920d7a35c6fb9e1d.webp?t=1761200550\" width=600 height=54 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Sometimes there are vicious Sea'Az that will attack you.<br>Let's work together with Axel and Rod to catch them!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2835110/extras/3dcdfeb2270fd504c76dc5a3918c6038.poster.avif?t=1761200550\" width=600 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2835110/extras/3dcdfeb2270fd504c76dc5a3918c6038.webm?t=1761200550\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2835110/extras/3dcdfeb2270fd504c76dc5a3918c6038.mp4?t=1761200550\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2835110/extras/a8ef4ad3c0289fdf55a251c1b147b726.poster.avif?t=1761200550\" width=600 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2835110/extras/a8ef4ad3c0289fdf55a251c1b147b726.webm?t=1761200550\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2835110/extras/a8ef4ad3c0289fdf55a251c1b147b726.mp4?t=1761200550\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2835110/extras/51044cb9d71f0dfca4228956fc6a0f64.webp?t=1761200550\" width=600 height=54 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Explore the vast pixel world freely by boat. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2835110/extras/c4f695108c9e200778757b0714d8e405.poster.avif?t=1761200550\" width=600 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2835110/extras/c4f695108c9e200778757b0714d8e405.webm?t=1761200550\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2835110/extras/c4f695108c9e200778757b0714d8e405.mp4?t=1761200550\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2835110/extras/861953184bc5addde7830ab908038f2f.webp?t=1761200550\" width=600 height=54 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >It is not only about fishing.<br>You can enjoy various 2D action elements in between fishing.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2835110/extras/9d2719964f0d7d1a2611a0c226a8dbc2.poster.avif?t=1761200550\" width=600 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2835110/extras/9d2719964f0d7d1a2611a0c226a8dbc2.webm?t=1761200550\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2835110/extras/9d2719964f0d7d1a2611a0c226a8dbc2.mp4?t=1761200550\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2835110/extras/f83f1e923d6e4ef4570051d638869d8e.poster.avif?t=1761200550\" width=600 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2835110/extras/f83f1e923d6e4ef4570051d638869d8e.webm?t=1761200550\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2835110/extras/f83f1e923d6e4ef4570051d638869d8e.mp4?t=1761200550\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2835110/extras/f4cb66c0e354673a535e1c8c1abe7c5a.poster.avif?t=1761200550\" width=600 height=120 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2835110/extras/f4cb66c0e354673a535e1c8c1abe7c5a.webm?t=1761200550\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2835110/extras/f4cb66c0e354673a535e1c8c1abe7c5a.mp4?t=1761200550\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Save the world by fishing!  A new pixel open world action RPG! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This is the story of two young men who set out on an adventure to fish for the Sea'Az, the marine creatures of this world. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2835110/extras/d9a465270c6318894a654acec47e9c1c.webp?t=1761200550\" width=600 height=54 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >To catch Sea'Az, perform a successful “Gauge Action”. If you stop the bar at the “Hit Area” or “Critical Area” in the gauge at the right time, you can damage Sea'Az. Successful fishing is achieved by continuing to inflict damage and reducing the HP to 0! Be careful, as there are SeaAZ with more powerful individual “gauge gimmick”.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2835110/extras/9e78d2977609086837522bcedf859946.poster.avif?t=1761200550\" width=600 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2835110/extras/9e78d2977609086837522bcedf859946.webm?t=1761200550\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2835110/extras/9e78d2977609086837522bcedf859946.mp4?t=1761200550\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2835110/extras/e0acde8da57916a16237a8d7b31e727a.webp?t=1761200550\" width=600 height=54 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You can create equipment (fishing rods and hooks) using materials obtained from the Sea'Az you catch. By creating strong equipment, you can take advantage of the fishing action.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2835110/extras/f50704538bd5bd307c2d0bb5426c1e2f.poster.avif?t=1761200550\" width=600 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2835110/extras/f50704538bd5bd307c2d0bb5426c1e2f.webm?t=1761200550\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2835110/extras/f50704538bd5bd307c2d0bb5426c1e2f.mp4?t=1761200550\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2835110/extras/d52f6a37922ee5d1e2d32df01b95db9e.webp?t=1761200550\" width=600 height=54 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Rod and Axel go on an adventurous journey together.<br>Let him do all the fishing for Sea'Az and stripping of materials.<br> Let Axel take care of everything, such as removing obstacles along the way.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2835110/extras/57b4671a7661b73b9c0a9fec5fa1ee47.poster.avif?t=1761200550\" width=600 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2835110/extras/57b4671a7661b73b9c0a9fec5fa1ee47.webm?t=1761200550\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2835110/extras/57b4671a7661b73b9c0a9fec5fa1ee47.mp4?t=1761200550\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2835110/extras/c4e9cccf4f4ee26f920d7a35c6fb9e1d.webp?t=1761200550\" width=600 height=54 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Sometimes there are vicious Sea'Az that will attack you.<br>Let's work together with Axel and Rod to catch them!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2835110/extras/3dcdfeb2270fd504c76dc5a3918c6038.poster.avif?t=1761200550\" width=600 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2835110/extras/3dcdfeb2270fd504c76dc5a3918c6038.webm?t=1761200550\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2835110/extras/3dcdfeb2270fd504c76dc5a3918c6038.mp4?t=1761200550\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2835110/extras/a8ef4ad3c0289fdf55a251c1b147b726.poster.avif?t=1761200550\" width=600 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2835110/extras/a8ef4ad3c0289fdf55a251c1b147b726.webm?t=1761200550\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2835110/extras/a8ef4ad3c0289fdf55a251c1b147b726.mp4?t=1761200550\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2835110/extras/51044cb9d71f0dfca4228956fc6a0f64.webp?t=1761200550\" width=600 height=54 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Explore the vast pixel world freely by boat. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2835110/extras/c4f695108c9e200778757b0714d8e405.poster.avif?t=1761200550\" width=600 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2835110/extras/c4f695108c9e200778757b0714d8e405.webm?t=1761200550\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2835110/extras/c4f695108c9e200778757b0714d8e405.mp4?t=1761200550\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2835110/extras/861953184bc5addde7830ab908038f2f.webp?t=1761200550\" width=600 height=54 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >It is not only about fishing.<br>You can enjoy various 2D action elements in between fishing.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2835110/extras/9d2719964f0d7d1a2611a0c226a8dbc2.poster.avif?t=1761200550\" width=600 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2835110/extras/9d2719964f0d7d1a2611a0c226a8dbc2.webm?t=1761200550\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steam